    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The problem is that subtests share a copy of the database, and also share the `makeBuild()` function and associated state including the build number. The subtests run in parallel, and so there is a race condition on the build number.\n\nAt a minimum, the subtests should not share a workspace, and should have their own build numbers.",
